snippet.title: MSX Longplay [041] Out Run (MSX1)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Eino

Maybe the worst port of Out Run? Very ugly and no sense of speed or control. Everything just appears in front at different pace. Touching any vehicle crashes the ferrari. But at least music could be worse. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
